Subject: drm/i915/psr: Write PSR2_MAN_TRK_CTL on DSB commit as well
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: e01cbca0ea603acd62dad647ec774e7a9e02a7a0
